     C*----------------------------------------------------*
     C*                   １画面                         *
     C*----------------------------------------------------*
     C                     MOVEL*DATE     @DATE   60
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $KOSIN
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $TOKU
